# Problem: Reverse Words in a String

## My Approach
I split the string into words after removing extra spaces, then reversed the order of words.

## Mistake
Initially, I thought of reversing the entire string which reversed characters instead of words.

## Final Logic
First remove leading and trailing spaces using strip().
Then split the string into words.
Reverse the list of words and join them with a single space.

## Pattern
String Manipulation (Split → Reverse → Join)

## Learning
Handling spaces correctly is important in string problems.
Reversing words is different from reversing characters.
